2пёЏвѓЈ Lab Preparation
Command:
lab start selfservice-projtemplate
What this command does internally:
It creates:
Resource	Purpose
user provisioner1	allowed to create projects
user provisioner2	allowed to create projects
group provisioners	group with permission
users added to group	provisioner1 & provisioner2
Verify group:
