рџ”џ Create Test Namespace
Now we design a LimitRange.
Create namespace:
oc create namespace template-test
Namespace is used only to design and test resources.
________________________________________
1пёЏвѓЈ1пёЏвѓЈ Create LimitRange
Edit file:
limitrange.yaml
Content:
apiVersion: v1
kind: LimitRange
metadata:
  name: max-memory
  namespace: template-test
spec:
  limits:
  - max:
      memory: 1Gi
    type: Container
Meaning:
Container cannot request more than 1Gi memory.
Create resource:
oc create -f limitrange.yaml
________________________________________
1пёЏвѓЈ2пёЏвѓЈ Test LimitRange
Deployment YAML requests:
memory: 2Gi
Create deployment:
oc create -f deployment.yaml -n template-test
Deployment is created.
But pods are not created.
Check pods:
oc get pod -n template-test
Output:
No resources found
________________________________________
1пёЏвѓЈ3пёЏвѓЈ Check Events
Command:
oc get events -n template-test
Message:
pods is forbidden:
maximum memory usage per container is 1Gi
but limit is 2Gi
Meaning:
LimitRange blocked pod creation.
